ich	 could	 alter	 the	 intellectual	 property	 protection	 regime	 in	 Europe.	 Nevertheless,	 the	 legislation,	 if implemented,	is	unlikely	to	significantly	impact	the	difficult	financial	situation	facing	many	Member	States	and	is,	therefore, not	likely	to	improve	the	overall	business	climate	for	biopharmaceutical	firms	operating	in	the	EU.

